    <node id="Statins">
      <data key="d0">Statins</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Statins are medications used to treat high LDL cholesterol, demonstrating the ability to lower cholesterol levels and reduce cardiovascular events.&lt;SEP&gt;Statins are a class of drugs used as first-line therapy to lower LDL cholesterol levels in patients who are allergic to or intolerant of statins.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21112bd6ed1fe7896dbf55a52bc45a2d</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1768894218</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus">
      <data key="d0">Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus is a prevalent form of diabetes that affects the body's ability to process blood sugar (glucose) effectively. This chronic condition is primarily characterized by insulin resistance, which may lead to impaired insulin secretion. As a result, individuals with Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus often experience elevated blood sugar levels. 

The condition is increasingly diagnosed in younger populations, particularly in the Eastern Mediterranean Region, where it has become more common due to the rising prevalence of obesity and associated lifestyle factors. Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus may not always require insulin for metabolic control, but it can be associated with various cardiovascular risk factors such as obesity and hypertension. 

Due to its asymptomatic nature in the early stages, Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus is often detected during routine health screenings. It is important for individuals diagnosed with this condition to undergo screenings for potential complications soon after diagnosis. The combination of insulin resistance and factors like obesity makes Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus a significant public health concern that necessitates awareness and proactive management.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d8c827cc2249067692290d6a8a0e8018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92fbe09a650e62b7b6ea5d8769440e51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b7df1782c359efe079f6ade12b3688f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12fe828372a20b6606e010f0fd5e6263&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25fb88c8ed14936954356d104de095d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5384df975133ef2a52113cd3ca0f897e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb0252816f7fbee4c50f79ef3ee56063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045</data>
