    <node id="Metabolic Syndrome">
      <data key="d0">Metabolic Syndrome</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Metabolic syndrome refers to a cluster of conditions, including insulin resistance, that increase the risk of heart disease and diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;Metabolic syndrome is a cluster of conditions increasing the risk of heart disease and diabetes, often identifiable by high blood pressure, high blood sugar, excess body fat, and abnormal cholesterol levels.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045</data>
