      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">The Oral Glucose Tolerance Test (OGTT) is a medical test to assess how the body processes glucose, crucial for diagnosing diabetes and gestational diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;The Oral Glucose Tolerance Test (OGTT) is the definitive confirmatory diagnostic test for diabetes mellitus, diagnosing diabetes at glucose levels ≥11.1 mmol/L.</data>
