      <data key="d0">Oral Anti-Diabetic Agents</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Oral anti-diabetic agents are medications used to manage type 2 diabetes, affecting insulin secretion and glucose absorption.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-eb0252816f7fbee4c50f79ef3ee56063</data>
